description: From the inside out—200g of PrimaLoft® Bio™ insulation and a B-DRY waterproof membrane—the Andesite is at home in ice-laden mountain towns. Featuring waterproof oiled nubuck leather, recycled components, and a Vibram Arctic Grip A.T. sole made of Vibram XS Trek.
name: Oboz Andesite Mid Insulated B-Dry - Mens
